  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to explore the relationship between deep brain stimulation
      implantation site and DTI (diffusion tensor imaging) derived measures for the region and
      later compare this to the clinical treatment outcomes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
